This paper involves the use of deep neural networks to analyze echocardiographic videos, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also involves the use of electronic health records (EHR) data, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the study involves the use of medical imaging, which falls under human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
